{"tid":85992,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係公司拍住d MK妹完全冇話題點算？","createTime":"2017-01-18T17:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T20:11:11.000Z","uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d5f134edd2ca1ec227b6266b2117a4f1ff328d1","tid":85992,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"份新工返左成半個月<br />\n都仲可以同班MK妹同事完全冇話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好話講話題就而傾d無聊野都冇<br />\n但佢地圍威餵一齊又可以吹到水<br />\n仲成日邊講邊笑鬼死咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我自己就好多時自己一個人做自己野唔同佢地吹水<br />\n好多時有d同事單丁拍住我<br />\n我完全feel到係佢地覺得我悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個仲成日黑面對住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時我遇到d客好騎呢好好笑<br />\n好想揾人分享下想笑鳩佢都冇人可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己就好似個傻仔咁自己笑係到自high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ne加係進化到d同事收工都唔會同我講拜拜(之前會，佢地會同其他同事講拜拜)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到我走既時候都係得我自己離開<br />\n想同佢地講拜拜都冇人會理我<br />\n所以我e加走既時候自己靜靜地離開<br />\n而拜拜都冇講聲就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a6c13726c53011e582c43b5a12a09505ee17b9","tid":85992,"uid":44176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"啪啪啪咗先咁就有話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4313029c8503363d3ca85db84a792e31b2805857","tid":85992,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T18:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啪啪啪咗先咁就有話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幻想過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有條女個身好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n